sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Page as Route Page
    participant Store as Zustand Store
    participant Client as Central API Client
    participant Storage as Browser Storage
    participant Backend as Rust API

    User->>Page: Trigger load or mutation
    Page->>Client: Call typed client method
    Client->>Storage: Use synchronized token and organization context
    alt Authenticated client method
        Client->>Backend: HTTP request with bearer and organization headers when available
    else Public client method
        Client->>Backend: HTTP request without bearer requirement
    end
    alt Successful JSON response
        Backend-->>Client: JSON response
        Client-->>Page: Generic result cast to manual TypeScript type
        Page-->>User: Render data or success status
    else Non-success response
        Backend-->>Client: Error status and response body
        Client-->>Page: Throw ApiError with status and message
        Page-->>User: Render page-local error status
    end

    Note over Page,Client: No automatic refresh retry, shared server-state cache, or runtime response validation was found
    Note over Store,Storage: Store actions synchronize reactive state, API module state, and localStorage
